## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of privacy legislation comprehensively. The rapidly evolving nature of privacy laws means that new regulations could emerge, potentially altering the current landscape. Additionally, the focus was primarily on U.S. laws, which may not be applicable in other jurisdictions.